    <id>https://2846807617frank-ops.github.io/2025/12/30/%E5%8A%A8%E8%A7%84%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%8D%E7%9B%98/</id>
    <link href="https://2846807617frank-ops.github.io/2025/12/30/%E5%8A%A8%E8%A7%84%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%8D%E7%9B%98/"/>
    <published>2025-12-30T10:00:00.000Z</published>
    <summary>
      <![CDATA[<p>计算机科学的问题很多时候是和数学紧密联系的。在解决线性递推数列和序列匹配问题时，单纯的模拟往往受限于时间复杂度。本文通过分析 <strong>P1962 斐波那契数列</strong> 和 <strong>P1439 最长公共子序列</strong>，探讨如何利用 <strong>线性代数</strong> 和 <strong>离散化映射</strong> 打破 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>N</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">O(N)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="strut" style="height:0.75em;"></span><span class="strut bottom" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="base textstyle uncramped"><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">O</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 和 O(n<sup>2</sup>) 的桎梏。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Problem Statement</strong>:<br>
<strong><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1962">P1962 斐波那契数列</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>来源</strong>: 暂无</li>
<li><strong>Algorithm</strong>: DP</li>
<li><strong>Difficulty</strong>: Green (普及+/提高)</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Problem Statement</strong>:<br>
<strong><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1439">P1439 最长公共子序列</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>来源</strong>: 暂无</li>
<li><strong>Algorithm</strong>: LCS,LIS</li>
<li><strong>Difficulty</strong>: Green (普及+/提高)</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>]]>
    </summary>
    <title>【算法笔记】从线性递推到映射转化：由 P1962 与 P1439 引发的数学思考</title>
    <updated>2025-12-30T03:02:58.326Z</updated>
