    <id>https://2846807617frank-ops.github.io/2025/12/29/%E3%80%90%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%8D%E7%9B%98%E3%80%91%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%B4%E5%88%B0%E9%AB%98%E7%BB%B4%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E8%B0%83%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%99%8D%E7%BB%B4%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2/</id>
    <link href="https://2846807617frank-ops.github.io/2025/12/29/%E3%80%90%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%8D%E7%9B%98%E3%80%91%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%B4%E5%88%B0%E9%AB%98%E7%BB%B4%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E8%B0%83%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%99%8D%E7%BB%B4%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2/"/>
    <published>2025-12-29T14:32:28.000Z</published>
    <summary>
      <![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p><strong>Problem Statement</strong>:<br>
<strong><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P2216">P2216 理想的正方形</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>来源</strong>: HAOI 2007 / Luogu</li>
<li><strong>Algorithm</strong>: Monotonic Queue, 2D RMQ</li>
<li><strong>Difficulty</strong>: Green (普及+/提高)</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p>在解决区间最值查询（Range Minimum/Maximum Query, RMQ）问题时，线段树和 ST 表常被视为标准解法。然而，当问题场景从静态转为动态滑动窗口，甚至扩展至二维矩阵时，<strong>单调队列 (Monotonic Queue)</strong> 凭借其 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>N</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">O(N)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="strut" style="height:0.75em;"></span><span class="strut bottom" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="base textstyle uncramped"><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">O</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 的线性复杂度，展现出了优于 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>N</mi><mi>log</mi><mi>N</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">O(N \log N)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="strut" style="height:0.75em;"></span><span class="strut bottom" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="base textstyle uncramped"><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">O</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mop">lo<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mord mathit" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 算法的工程美学。</p>
<p>本文以 <strong>P2216 [HAOI2007] 理想的正方形</strong> 为例，复盘我如何利用“降维思想”将二维 RMQ 问题拆解为两次一维扫描。</p>]]>
    </summary>
    <title>【算法复盘】从一维到高维：利用单调队列进行降维搜索</title>
    <updated>2025-12-30T01:59:21.073Z</updated>
  </entry>
